@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yxksmg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((v1 - (v2 + 0.11 / tmp + 0.33)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(tmp) / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.96) / 0.99))
    v2 = 0.55
    v2 = v1
    v0 = v0
    tmp = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.95 / v0 + 0.94) + 0.74))
    v0 = (0.01 + (tmp - (tmp + 0.83 * v0 + 0.85)))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
